() Tj
T*
(Runtime normalization policy \(performance\)) Tj
T*
(- Base56 is treated as an edge-format \(UI/API boundary\).) Tj
T*
(- At entry points, addresses are normalized once to canonical HPK \(normalize_hpk\).) Tj
T*
(- Storage and transaction internals operate HPK-only for matching and indexing.) Tj
T*
(- Result: less repeated string conversion in hot loops \(UTXO scans, send path, selection\), with) Tj
T*
(no consensus rule change.) Tj
T*
ET
